難到我？<br />\n<br />\n老細都話我進步左好多<br />\n<br />\n我將自己經歷融入自己個故度<br />\n「得到無用超能力的廢物公主」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事的公主知道自己終極的命運：<br />\n勞碌終日，橫屍荒野<br />\n<br />\n但係調轉講，即係佢唔去荒野就有不死身。<br />\n<br />\n有時候，加少少創意<br />\n<br />\n好多負面的野都可以諗得無咁灰<br />\n<br />\n我而加希望我的不幸變成別人祝福<br />\n<br />\n樓主，加油呀<br />\n<br />\n尤其ptsd黎料的時候，搵人傾下啦，支持你"},{"pid":"2132ccd886cbca4061cfc0cfcd1feb5c449e1f46","tid":2062017,"uid":2342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82fe7f5a2570888eaf9e6c95ccffca39355948a4","tid":2062017,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:14:22.000Z","msg":"已經做定身後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:27:17.000Z","msg":"準備做，驚太突然無野留低比身邊既人<br />\n除左遺書（每個較close既朋友都有一封）<br />\n仲打算去影張靚靚韓式證件相做車頭相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果到時車頭相係我中小學啲學生相<br />\n我應該會係棺材到彈返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b9e5a1b8bf1dd70fe8d6c6b928240f6ee193cf","tid":2062017,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2132ccd886cbca4061cfc0cfcd1feb5c449e1f46","tid":2062017,"uid":2342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82fe7f5a2570888eaf9e6c95ccffca39355948a4","tid":2062017,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:14:22.000Z","msg":"已經做定身後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:27:17.000Z","msg":"準備做，驚太突然無野留低比身邊既人<br />\n除左遺書（每個較close既朋友都有一封）<br />\n仲打算去影張靚靚韓式證件相做車頭相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果到時車頭相係我中小學啲學生相<br />\n我應該會係棺材到彈返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T00:32:38.000Z","msg":"你係獨生子/女？<br />\n頭有無兄弟姊妹分擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif